title: Chia Seed Omelette
directions: Beat eggs for 2 minutes then add sea salt and black pepper.
Pour olive oil into a hot pan then add baby spinach, tomatoes and chia seeds.
Add egg mixture on top of other ingredients and swirl until thinly covered (cook on medium heat).
Fold egg mixture over and turn heat off.
Serve with extra baby spinach or rye toast and enjoy!
